tc.research_page.COREFISHING.2=      §n傀儡升级:风解锁§r<IMG>thaumcraft:textures/items/golem_upgrade_air.png:0:0:255:255:0.0625</IMG>装有这种升级的傀儡有小几率能一次抓到不止一条鱼.
tc.research_page.COREFISHING.3=      §n傀儡升级:火解锁§r<IMG>thaumcraft:textures/items/golem_upgrade_fire.png:0:0:255:255:0.0625</IMG>安装这种升级的傀儡会自动烹饪它抓住的鱼.
tc.research_page.COREFISHING.4=     §n傀儡升级:秩序解锁§r<IMG>thaumcraft:textures/items/golem_upgrade_order.png:0:0:255:255:0.0625</IMG>秩序升级会提高钓到大鱼的概率.
tc.research_page.COREFISHING.5=    §n傀儡升级:混沌解锁§r<IMG>thaumcraft:textures/items/golem_upgrade_entropy.png:0:0:255:255:0.0625</IMG>混沌升级会减少钓到廉价物品的概率.
